summary:
A brand new orcish hut resource based on the Orcish longhouses, perfect for young orcs looking for a starter home. contains Interior, exterior and LOD materials.

This is not a house mod, only the resources needed to build one.
descriptionHtml:
A brand new orcish house (hut) resource based on the architecture of the Orcish longhouses.

This is a small Orcish house modelled by me, as a Skyrim Modders resource. I always felt that Skyrim lacked in Orcish architecture and I hope this resource will give the community something new to play with.

For info on future releases and other updates about Beyond Skyrim, like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BeyondSkyrim

Be sure to read the readme.
author: Markus Liberty
